|- scripts
|  |- bootstrap.sh  (install dependencies and setup environment)
|  \- setup.sh      (symbolic link dotfiles to $HOME)
|- dotfiles
|  \- [dotfiles arranged to simulate their structure relative to $HOME]
\- nixos
   \- [all nix flakes, nixos configurations, home manager configurations]

- all files are symlinked from dotfiles to $HOME, any dots preceding a file are substituted with an _
